  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: Morphine infusion decreases time to mechanical ventilation weaning and
      extubation, as compared to the combination of fentanyl and midazolam in critically-ill
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
